[FMD can affect human beings, but it is relatively harmless, much like a
bad cold virus. There have been approximately 40 documented human cases
since 1921.
We would like to know the strain of the current outbreak. Is it O, A, or C?
- Mod.TG
[For those interested in the issue of FMD transmission to humans, see
Bauer, K. 1997. Foot-and-mouth disease as zoonosis. Arch Virol Suppl.
13:95-7. - Man. Ed. DS
